e 6h43, 7h14 et 7h27 au d&#233;part de Dourdan.<br><br>Avant de vous rendre en gare, nous vous recommandons de v&#233;rifier l&#8217;horaire de votre train sur  :<br>l'appli Ile-de France Mobilit&#233;s, le site Transilien.com, SNCF Connect ou votre appli de mobilit&#233;.<br><br>Motif : Trains retenus en atelier de maintenance<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01727","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:60247","name":"Brétigny (Brétigny-sur-Orge)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71135","name":"Gare d'Austerlitz (Paris)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01727","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:71135","name":"Gare d'Austerlitz (Paris)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:60247","name":"Brétigny (Brétigny-sur-Orge)"}}],"disruption_id":"f03a2e4a-0f2d-11f1-b9dd-0a58a9feac02"},{"id":"f5fb1e67-caf1-4a7b-ba75-d37b1092f4e3","applicationPeriods":[{"begin":"20260322T125511","end":"20260322T143000"}],"lastUpdate":"20260322T130103","cause":"PERTURBATION","severity":"PERTURBEE","title":"RER D : Goussainville <-> Melun trafic ralenti","message":"<p>Le trafic est ralenti entre Goussainville et Melun dans les 2 sens.<\/p><p>Pr&#233;voir des allongements de temps de trajet allant jsuqu'&#224; 15 minutes ainsi que des modificatiosn du plan de transport.&nbsp;<br><br>Pour plus d'informations sur cette perturbation, consultez le <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/RERD_SNCF\">fil X du RER D<\/a>.<br><br>Motif : accident de personne dans le secteur de Boussy-Saint-Antoine.<\/p>","shortMessage":"Trafic perturbé","impactedSections":[{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01728","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:66535","name":"Goussainville (Goussainville)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:61926","name":"Melun (Melun)"}},{"lineId":"line:IDFM:C01728","from":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:61926","name":"Melun (Melun)"},"to":{"type":"stop_area","id":"stop_area:IDFM:66535","name":"Goussai